    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a solid choice for someone looking for a dependable daily driver. While the mechanical components are in good working order, the car does show its age with some noticeable exterior scratches and minor dings. Inside, the upholstery shows signs of regular wear, and some of the plastic trim has faded over time. However, it has been regularly serviced and remains a functional, budget-friendly option for any commuter.",
